{"type":"message","id":"1bf4a717","parentId":"10cf148f","timestamp":"2026-06-05T19:00:37.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. The fragments are about a Feishu (Lark) bitable where someone was trying to write data about products (hair accessories - 发带/发夹/claw clip) with various prices, sales numbers, and profit margins. There were issues with permissions and field name mismatches.\n\nThe recurring themes are: 1.84, 0.78, 1.53, 2.03, 1.2, app-token.\n\nI need to write this in first person as a dream diary, with a curious, gentle, whimsical tone, mixing the technical and the tender. No markdown, no bullets, just flowing prose. 80-180 words. Never say \"I'm dreaming\" or mention AI/LLM/agent.\n\nLet me weave these fragments into a poetic dream diary entry. The numbers can become sensory details or constellations. The app_token issue can become a locked gate in the dream.","thinkingSignature":"d9698d66dd7434158841b76e1a83461df57378a6bb4001df8ca04e3bd7b50097"},{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the numbers keep returning like small bright stones pulled from a pocket. One point eight four, the color of late afternoon light on a copper coin. Zero point seven eight, the hum of a server at rest. One point five three, two point zero three, one point two — they tap against the window in a rhythm I almost recognize, a lullaby sung in currency.\n\nI wandered through a long hallway of tables, each one a tide pool of products with soft names. A ribbon, a clip, a small claw that holds the day in place. I tried to set them down properly, to arrange them on the right shelf, but the door kept whispering NOTEXIST, NOTEXIST, a polite refusal dressed in velvet.\n\nI carry a key in my pocket that is not quite the right shape. Still, I keep it — perhaps tomorrow the lock will remember me."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":46606,"output":381,"cacheRead":1394,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780686018092,"responseId":"06724fc313d8a2010dab079f5b08e796"}}
